description: This spacious bi-level 3-bedroom, 3 bathroom condo offers a comfortable living experience with its 1,856 square feet of beautifully designed space. Step inside and feel instantly at home with the open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen is a chef’s delight, equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage for all your culinary needs. The bedrooms are roomy and inviting, providing the perfect retreat after a busy day. The primary suite features an ensuite bathroom, offering a perfect spot to unwind. A bonus office/second Living Room can be found in the lower level. Complete with washer and dryer in unit, central AC, storage room and 1 DEEDED Parking Spot.
